The paper deals with the estimation and prediction of wireless channels, which is a common topic in the information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI) communities. The use of multiple antennas and OFDM also suggests a potential fit with the signal processing (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper derives a closed-form expression for the error bound, which could be of interest to researchers in the machine learning (cs.LG) community.
